  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK760">
<l>oṇporuḷ kāḻppa viyaṟṟiyārk keṇporu</l>
<l>ḷēṉai yiraṇṭu moruṅku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To those who have honestly acquired an abundance of riches, the other two, (virtue and pleasure) are things easy (of acquisition).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
